Sec. 102-71.4. - Off-street parking and loading requirements.
Off-street parking and loading requirements pertaining to uses allowed in this district shall conform with the
provisions of article VI - Off-Street Parking and Loading Requirements.
llm_outputs.rationale: The section titled 'Off-street parking and loading requirements' refers to the parking requirements for the district, which are detailed in article VI of the same document.
